<!-- ABOUT NSIA -->
<section class="about fade-up" id="about">
    <div class="about-text">
        <div class="section-label">About NSIA</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Nigeria's Sovereign Wealth Fund Manager</h2>
        <p>The Nigeria Sovereign Investment Authority (NSIA) is an independent investment institution of the Federation, established by Act of the National Assembly in May 2011. It manages Nigeria's sovereign wealth fund — investing surplus oil revenues for the long-term benefit of all Nigerians.</p>
        <p>With over $2.4 billion in assets under management, NSIA is the third largest sovereign wealth fund in Sub-Saharan Africa, operating three ring-fenced funds each serving a distinct national mandate.</p>
        <div class="about-pillars">
            <div class="pillar p1"><div class="pillar-name">Financial Sustainability</div><div class="pillar-desc">Maximising risk-adjusted returns on invested assets</div></div>
            <div class="pillar p2"><div class="pillar-name">Independence</div><div class="pillar-desc">Impartial, merit-based investment decisions</div></div>
            <div class="pillar p3"><div class="pillar-name">Transparency</div><div class="pillar-desc">Consistent financial reporting and public accountability</div></div>
            <div class="pillar p4"><div class="pillar-name">National Impact</div><div class="pillar-desc">Driving socioeconomic outcomes across key sectors</div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="funds-grid">
            <div class="fund-card f1"><div class="fund-icon">🏦</div><div><div class="fund-name">Stabilisation Fund</div><div class="fund-desc">Provides budget support and fiscal buffers during periods of economic stress, ensuring government services remain uninterrupted.</div></div></div>
            <div class="fund-card f2"><div class="fund-icon">🌱</div><div><div class="fund-name">Future Generations Fund</div><div class="fund-desc">An intergenerational savings vehicle investing in long-term assets so future Nigerians benefit from today's oil wealth.</div></div></div>
            <div class="fund-card f3"><div class="fund-icon">🏗️</div><div><div class="fund-name">Nigeria Infrastructure Fund</div><div class="fund-desc">Finances critical infrastructure — from toll roads and power projects to healthcare centres — that attract investment and create jobs.</div></div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- NPI PROGRAMME -->
<section class="npi-section" id="programme">
    <div class="npi-inner">
        <div class="programme-intro fade-up">
            <div class="programme-intro-left">
                <div class="section-label">The Programme</div>
                <h2 class="section-heading">NSIA Prize for Innovation</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="programme-intro-right">
                <p>A multi-year programme designed to fund, mentor, and accelerate early-stage Nigerian digital innovations — from first idea to global-ready startup.</p>
                <p>We back bold innovators solving real problems in three critical sectors. If your solution drives measurable impact in healthcare, agriculture, or climate and ESG, this programme is for you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sectors-wrap fade-up">
